# Vercel Ignore
# Files to exclude from Vercel deployment

# Archives
archive/

# Development
node_modules/
*.log
.env.local
.env.development

# Old files
frontend/

# Documentation (optional - remove if you want docs deployed)
*.md
!README.md

# Cache
.cache/
.vite/

# Tests
*.test.*
*.spec.*

# CI/CD (not needed in deployment)
.github/

